{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that same thing happened that morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were pre-warned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we lived at the far end of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CLEARING THROAT] So we got ready to go into the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not quite a year. it was less than a year.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, uh-- So I was very proud of this hiding place that we had in the basement.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father says, I'm not going to crawl like a dog to go into that place, because he had to get on all four to get into this hiding place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I was very hurt because he didn't appreciate the huge effort that I made because we had to close off a wall.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we have two plaster it and paint it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other wall we had to dust with coal dust in order to make it look old and stuff.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a really good hiding place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only thing that wasn't very strong with it was that we didn't have enough air in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went in there and we started sitting and seeing how it feels to be in there, and the candlelight went out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we realized that there was not enough oxygen so we had to make a large opening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then it became academic, because when we got to the-- when we finally decided to go into hiding, we went to the hiding place, the hiding place was full.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Other people heard about the-- knew about the hiding place and they took that place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went into the second axillary hiding place, which was not as safe, but it was still-- it was in the roof space.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was August.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very hot day, and we were sitting, water was running from us.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
